<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>彭博加密货币</title><link>https://bloomberg.com/crypto/</link><description>彭博加密货币</description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 20 Mar 2026 01:06:21 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>Winklevosses 称 Gemini Exchange 裁员人数达到 30%</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-19/winklevosses-says-jobs-cuts-at-gemini-exchange-reach-30</link><description>自年初裁员以来，Gemini Space Station Inc. 的员工人数已减少约 30%，该加密货币交易所周四表示，正在部署人工智能工具以提高生产力。该公司去年亏损超过 5 亿美元。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iVKjfCCj1wqo/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Mar 2026 22:00:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-19/winklevosses-says-jobs-cuts-at-gemini-exchange-reach-30</guid></item><item><title>数字信贷是加密货币财务公司杠杆的最新代号</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2026-03-19/digital-credit-is-the-latest-code-word-for-leverage-among-crypto-dats</link><description>数字资产国债越来越多地转向信贷市场。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iNHrjc.FVWS8/v7/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Mar 2026 21:08:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2026-03-19/digital-credit-is-the-latest-code-word-for-leverage-among-crypto-dats</guid></item><item><title>石油价格上涨冲击风险资产，比特币难以守住 70,000 美元</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-19/bitcoin-dips-below-70-000-as-energy-prices-surge</link><description>由于中东能源基础设施再次遭受攻击，市场大范围抛售，比特币价格一周多以来首次跌破 70,000 美元。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iKVCTkfcyAFQ/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Mar 2026 08:36:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-19/bitcoin-dips-below-70-000-as-energy-prices-surge</guid></item><item><title>前妻离婚后被指控盗窃 1.8 亿英镑比特币</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-19/ex-wife-accused-of-stealing-180-million-in-bitcoin-after-divorce</link><description>离婚后，一名丈夫指控前妻密谋盗窃价值数百万美元的比特币和豪华手表，此案将考验英国民事法院如何对待数字资产。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iVvrnnfg0iIU/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Mar 2026 10:01:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-19/ex-wife-accused-of-stealing-180-million-in-bitcoin-after-divorce</guid></item><item><title>随着避险情绪上升，比特币三周来跌幅最大</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-18/bitcoin-retreats-from-six-week-high-as-iran-conflict-escalates</link><description>由于伊朗紧张局势升级引发全球市场广泛避险情绪，比特币创下三周以来最大跌幅。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ic.B_Ak0Wghs/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Mar 2026 14:18:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-18/bitcoin-retreats-from-six-week-high-as-iran-conflict-escalates</guid></item><item><title>人工智能、加密货币在伊利诺伊州初选中遭遇意外失败</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-18/ai-crypto-suffer-surprise-defeats-in-illinois-primary-fights</link><description>伊利诺伊州的民主党选民本周拒绝了加密货币和人工智能行业支持的大多数候选人，这标志着资金雄厚的特殊利益集团在准备花费数亿美元在今年的中期选举中塑造国会时意外失败。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i.DGru0nGTno/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Mar 2026 15:05:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-18/ai-crypto-suffer-surprise-defeats-in-illinois-primary-fights</guid></item><item><title>美国和其他国家寻求影响力，敦促英国禁止加密货币捐赠</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-18/uk-urged-to-ban-crypto-donations-as-us-and-others-seek-influence</link><description>由于人们越来越担心包括美国在内的外国的影响，英国立法者正在推动政府立法禁止向政党捐赠加密货币。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iQGpBIg3B6wY/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Mar 2026 13:55:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-18/uk-urged-to-ban-crypto-donations-as-us-and-others-seek-influence</guid></item><item><title>蓬勃发展的加密货币交易所在“TradFi”推送中获得标准普尔官方数据</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-18/booming-crypto-exchange-gets-official-s-p-data-in-tradfi-push</link><description>几十年来，标准普尔全球公司的指数部门一直向受监管的金融界中坚力量授予全球最受关注的股票基准的许可。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iKko44gQT9Sc/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Mar 2026 13:30:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-18/booming-crypto-exchange-gets-official-s-p-data-in-tradfi-push</guid></item></channel></rss>